# What time is Strictly Come Dancing on tonight? The exact start time for tonight's result show
Who will end up in the dance off?
By [Amy May Ellis](/uk/author/429527/amy-may-ellis/)Updated: 12 October 2025*With [Strictly Come Dancing](https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/entertainment/g65311878/strictly-come-dancing-2025-line-up/)* in full swing, weekends can't come around fast enough, and in classic *Strictly *fashion, the show has started with no shortage of drama. From [Amber Davies](https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/entertainment/a68071172/strictly-come-dancing-2025-amber-davies-joins-line-up/) filling in for Dani Dyer at the last minute, to [Diane Buswell's pregnancy](https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/entertainment/a67979786/strictly-come-dancing-2025-dianne-buswell-take-part-pregnancy/), this season is set to be a good one.
Tonight's results show is a particularly fun one as we find out who's safe and who's at risk after the first themed week of the series: movie week! Stars took on iconic roles from *Barbie *to *James **Bond*, and Cynthia Evro blessed our screens as the show's first-ever guest mentor. But after some scheduling changes to last night's live show, when are tonight's results actually on? 

## Jump to:


- [What time is Strictly on tonight?](#what-time-is-strictly-on-tonight)

- [What time is Strictly usually on?](#what-time-is-strictly-usually-on)

- [When is It Takes Two on?](#when-is-it-takes-two-on)

- [When is the Strictly final?](#when-is-the-strictly-final)

BBC
## What time is *Strictly *on tonight?
**The *Strictly *results show is on at **7:15pm tonight, 12th October**.
It's on after *Hamza's Hidden Wild Isles*, and runs for 45 minutes. If you don't manage to catch the show live, no worries! It will be available on BBC iPlayer to watch at your leisure. 

## What time is *Strictly *usually on?
Saturday's *Strictly *live **show is usually on at 6:30pm every week.
Advertisement - Continue Reading Below
## When is *It Takes Two* on?
If you can't wait a whole week for your *Strictly *fix, *It Takes Two* is the perfect place for all the backstage gossip, and thankfully, it's on every weeknight at 6:30pm.

## When is the Strictly final?
This year, the *Strictly *final takes place on December 20th, a week later than previous seasons. With it being so early into the competition, it's hard to know who might end up lifting the glitterball trophy, and there might still be time for a dark horse to steal the race!
